Note,

The **vertical displacement of Ball 2 matches the vertical displacement of Ball 1**.

The **vertical displacement and vertical velocity** of Ball 2 are only affected by the vertical acceleration \(\mathbf{g}\) (as in Ball 1).

\(\circ\) **Horizontal Motion:**

Consider the motion of Ball 2. Note that

The **horizontal displacements** made by the ball at equal intervals of time are approximately the same.

