**Advantages of Geostationary Satellites**

1. As they remain stationary above the same point on Earth, they are ideal for use as communication satellites as they require no tracking to receive signals from Earth. This is why there is no need to keep adjusting the satellite dish to receive TV signals from a particular geostationary satellite.

