\[B=\frac{\mu_{o}NI}{2r}\]

where \(\mu_{o}\) is the **permeability of free space** which has the value 4\(\mathrm{\SIUnitSymbolMicro x}\)\(10^{-7}\)\(\mathrm{H}\)\(\mathrm{m}^{-1}\).

